snippet.title: Shufflepuck Cafe (1989) MS-DOS PC Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Despite its 16-color engine, this game was arguably the first of its kind. That made it the legend to be remembered, at least as for me. Developed by Ubisoft.

LINK TO GET THE GAME: http://adf.ly/Q7ScR
